0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\">wakamiti <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">wakamiti -d</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"-c---clean\"><a href=\"#-c---clean\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">-c</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">--clean</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">boolean</code> (flag)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Cleans local cache before downloading modules.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\">wakamiti <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-c</span></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">wakamiti -c</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"-f---file\"><a href=\"#-f---file\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">-f</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">--file</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">file</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code class=\"language-text\">wakamiti.yaml</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Specifies the configuration file to load.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\">wakamiti <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> wakamiti.ci.yaml</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">wakamiti -f wakamiti.ci.yaml</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"-m---modules\"><a href=\"#-m---modules\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">-m</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">--modules</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">string[]</code> (comma-separated)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Adds modules from CLI 